CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: PetMed Express Inc along with its subsidiaries is a nationwide pet pharmacy. The company markets prescription and non-prescription pet medications, health products, and supplies for dogs and cats, direct to the consumer. The company generates its revenue by selling pet medications and pet supplies primarily to retail consumers.
